Title: AjaxForWinForms
Description:
It's purpose is to have the Ajax controls on Windows Forms
It's developed in C#
HomeWiki:
This project aims at releasing at Windows Forms the same controls as the Asp.Net Ajax Controls Toolkit
The first release is TextBoxWatermark
